{"tid":2517202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉包圍屯門大興基地 4人被控非法集結 警員莫冠斌:正常人如果冇犯事 點解見到警察走?","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:39:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c381b6ce9ef08293aa80faa49fb841740c58ccd","tid":2517202,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"前年 10 月屯門多處傳出不明氣體，過百名市民到警方大興行動基地抗議，期間發生警民衝突。4 名男女包括前年屯門區議會選舉候選人張贊華，被控非法集結等罪，今（5 日）在屯門裁判法院續審。拘捕首被告的警員莫冠斌供稱，在場人士並非身體不適才戴口罩，是為逃避警方追捕。他又稱正常人不會在非法集結地方逗留，「唔覺得正常人會喺嗰度行街或休息」、「如果作為一個冇犯事嘅人，點解見到警察要走？」<br />\n<br />\n警員莫冠斌今午離開屯門裁判法院時，有記者上前拍攝，他隨即表示：「影多啲，影多啲，唔該。」<br />\n<br />\n莫冠斌隸屬新界北快速應變部隊第 3 隊，他供稱當晚到屯門大興行動基地支援，在附近掃蕩不果，晚上 10 時半返回震寰路及良運路交界設立防線，目睹至少 100 人聚集。大部分人戴口罩，並用垃圾桶堵路、向警方掟雜物及照射鐳射光，期間叫囂及高呼口號，如「光復香港，時代革命」。<br />\n<br />\n莫續指晚上 11 時 38 分驅散示威者，他追截期間，在海麗花園及「珀御」之間的無名路，見到首被告站在路口，身旁有數十名戴口罩的人。他們看到警員隨即四散，被告跑往輕鐵路軌，莫當時與她相距 10 米。被告跑到「珀御」附近燈柱時跌倒，一度試圖逃走，莫趕到將她制服。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B6%89%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%88%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0-4-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E5%86%87%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%8B-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B5%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0-4-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25B5%25B0%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=c901b6da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0-4-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25B5%25B0%2F&h=fef1bffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B6%89%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%88%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0-4-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E5%86%87%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%8B-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B5%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"71fc780b685dbdfc7e4aa53860d392923d4c3d88","tid":2517202,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191222/GOEALHSSKVRUMDXAERJH35FD4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2FGOEALHSSKVRUMDXAERJH35FD4Q%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=092d29a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2FGOEALHSSKVRUMDXAERJH35FD4Q%2F&h=02527cce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191222/GOEALHSSKVRUMDXAERJH35FD4Q/</a><br />\n因為唔行開就會比班狗撞<br />\n你見到街邊d野狗係咁吠都會行開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}